org.neontoolkit.registry.oyster2
Interface QueryReplyListener

All Known Implementing Classes:
Reply, ResultAPI
public interface QueryReplyListener

The listener interface for receiving notification about new Query Replys. Everytime a new message is received the newQueryReply() method would be used to inform all listeners.
